{"tid":123480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"撐警者庭外展示辱罵法官標語「狗品支那官」","createTime":"2017-02-17T01:57:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-18T03:07:10.000Z","uid":20933,"like":96,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"abfab584cf871f19c3794106664c23dfc869e8f7","tid":123480,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T01:57:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170217/large/1487293375_2363.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170217%2Flarge%2F1487293375_2363.jpg&h=3c59802a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n7名警員於佔領期間在添馬公園變電站暗角位置，毆打公民黨前成員曾健超，7人於周二被裁定襲擊致他人受傷罪成，第5被告則因於警署掌摑曾健超而另被裁定普通襲擊罪成。法官今早將判刑，有撐警組織到場，並展示辱罵法官的標語。<br />\n<br />\n7名被告依序為有組織罪案及三合會調查科總督察黃祖成（49歲）、觀塘區反黑組高級督察劉卓毅（30歲）、觀塘區反黑組警長白榮斌（43歲）、觀塘區反黑 組警員劉興沛（39歲）、東九龍總區刑事總部警員陳少丹（32歲）、九龍城區刑事偵緝警員關嘉豪（33歲）及觀塘區反黑組警員黃偉豪（37歲）。"},{"pid":"2f2d90b6e971edead68367e1af353c133fa0ec96","tid":123480,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T01:58:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170217/large/1487292781_6bf3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170217%2Flarge%2F1487292781_6bf3.jpg&h=1a3d753a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170217/large/1487292780_d861.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170217%2Flarge%2F1487292780_d861.jpg&h=793898d0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"72c0f12ab798091170a2a0529ab0809fecbc2038","tid":123480,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T01:58:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170217&amp;guid=56315115&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/li